data.description: Come see this cozy, well-maintained, 3-bedroom / 2-bathroom home located in the Porter’s Meadow Community. This home features an open floor plan with a large backyard and no rear neighbors. The primary bedroom is spacious and features a large walk-in closet with plenty of storage space. Home is located within a few minutes of schools, shopping and local restaurants. Refrigerator, Washer and Dryer will convey.
